headline: McCormick (MKC) Q2 Earnings Top Estimates
summary: McCormick (MKC) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +6.15% and -0.22%, respectively, for the quarter ended May 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
